ous and more measurable as part of the fabric of britain we can see first hand the challenges britain faces through our operations and our  colleagues the plan is core to our strategy we know from long experience that when britain prospers we do too so the plan is an investment in our collective longterm success it supports our strategy to become the best bank for customers and it’s fundamental to rebuilding trust in our brands and sector download helping britain prosper plan  view now our targets people businesses and communities across britain are facing significant challenges we’re helping to address them through our helping britain prosper plan we believe no other bank is better placed to do this we already serve approximately  million customers and  million small businesses but we want to be more than a bank we want to go beyond business as usual and help address systemic social and economic challenges such as britain’s housing shortage the skills gap in key industries social mobility and social disadvantage our targets fall naturally into three categories reflecting our desire to help people businesses and communities across britain download helping britain prosper plan  plan on a page view now plan performance in  we achieved  of our  targets we provided  in  new build mortgages we invested over £m in house builders we created over  new apprenticeships we supported  startups we raised £m for bbc children in need download helping britain prosper plan    performance view now sara weller qa sara weller chair of our responsible business committee answers questions about the helping britain prosper plan and our performance as a responsible business in  “helping britain prosper is about creating opportunities for all to share in the economic and social benefits of a successful uk as a sustainable lowrisk business we can support this success in many ways”   download qa with sara weller view now our impact people code club inspiring the next generation of coders busi