es midmarkets corporates and financial institutions the consumer finance segment offers motor finance credit cards and unsecured personal loans with its european business to consumers and commercial customers the insurance segment provides longterm savings and investment and money protection products as well as home insurance motor insurance and life pension products the company also provides personal and business loans lloyds banking group plc was founded in  and is headquartered in london the united kingdomcorporate governancelloyds banking group plc’s iss governance qualityscore as of july   is  the pillar scores are audit  board  shareholder rights  compensation corporate governance scores courtesy of institutional shareholder services iss scores indicate decile rank relative to index or region a decile score of  indicates lower governance risk while a  indicates higher governance riskyahoo small businessdata disclaimerhelpsuggestionsprivacyabout our adsterms updated lloyds banking group plc lloylse summary  ftcom subscribe sign in menu search financial times myft search the ft search search the ft search close marketsmarkets dataequities financial timesclosesearch theftsearch equities lloyds banking group plclloylseselect symbolunited kingdomlloylselondon stock exchangellpclselondon stock exchangellpdlselondon stock exchangellpelselondon stock exchangellpglselondon stock exchangellpjlselondon stock exchangellphlselondon stock exchangelldlselondon stock exchangelldlselondon stock exchangelldlselondon stock exchangelldlselondon stock exchangevslselondon stock exchangelldlselondon stock exchangelldlselondon stock exchangellpcgbisdintercapital icap securities and derivatives excllpdgbisdintercapital icap securities and derivatives excunited stateslldtfpkcotc pink  current informationlygnyqnyselygnysnysegermanylldberberlin stock exchangellddusdusseldorf stock exchangelldxgerxetra level lldmunmunich stock exchangelldstustuttgart stock exchangelloydeugerman compositel