d offer a range of financial products and services such as current accounts savings mortgages loans credit cards to private banking and wealth management services birmingham midshires offers savings solutions and specialist mortgages for buytolet and selfbuild through mortgage advisors ldc is a midmarket private equity house scottish widows product range includes life cover critical illness income protection pensions annuities savings and investment products customers can access scottish widows products and services through independent financial advisors directly and through all lloyds bank bank of scotland and halifax branchesretailthe retail segment offers a range of financial service products including current accounts savings and mortgages to the united kingdom personal customers including wealth and small business customers it is also a distributor of insurance and a range of longterm savings and investment productscommercial bankingthe commercial banking segment supports the united kingdom businesses from small and mediumsized enterprises smes to large corporates and financial institutions it provides clients with a range of products and services such as lending transactional banking working capital management risk management debt capital markets services as well as access to private equity through lloyds development capitalconsumer financethe consumer finance segment offers consumer lending products including motor finance credit cards and unsecured personal loans along with its european business it also includes black horse and lex autolease as well as its mortgage and deposit taking businesses in germany and the netherlands its cards business is made up of consumer credit cards commercial cards and cardnet cardnet enables retailers and merchants to accept electronic payments for their goods and services it offers unsecured personal loans to franchise customers across its three retail brands black horse provides motor finance loans to finance new and used cars caravans motor homes and motorbikes lex autolease is a fleet management and leasing specialist which manages more than  cars and commercial vehicles across the united kingdominsurancethe insurance segment provides a range of protection pension and investment products to meet the needs of its customers the insurance segment consists of life pensions and investments business and provides longterm savings protection and investment products its products are offered through financial advisers and through its retail segment through the brands of lloyds bank halifax bank of scotland and scottish widows the general insurance business provides home insurance in the united kingdom with products sold through its branches direct channels and corporate partners » full overview of lyg company address lloyds banking group plc  gresham streetlondon     ecv hn p  company web links home page officers  directors name compensation norman blackwell  antonio hortaosorio  anita frew  george culmer  antonio lorenzo  » more officers  directors lloyds banking group plc news lloyds bank makes offers on compensation for fraud after delay jul   bank of england opens up payments systems to spur fintech jul   bank of england opens up payments systems to spur fintech jul   uk financial watchdog combines hbos investigations jul   lloyds bank to reduce cost of overdrafts after criticism jul   » more lyg news related topics stocksstock screenerfinancialsbanks investors  performance  lloyds banking group plc skip to content home accessibility information site map by using wwwlloydsbankinggroupcom you agree to the outlined use of cookies in our cookie notice close share price share price info toggle navigation home investors  performance investors  performance lloyds banking group financial results investor news and shareholder information our strengths and capabilities provide significant advantage and differentiation driving value creation helping britain prosper plan helping people business and c